# Program 1 â€” Windows 10 STIG V3R1 Remediation

## Objective

This program demonstrates structured remediation and automation of 10 failed controls from the Microsoft Windows 10 STIG V3R1 baseline.

The goal is to simulate an enterprise compliance remediation lifecycle rather than isolated configuration changes.

---

## Environment

- Azure Windows 10 Virtual Machine
- Tenable.io Compliance Scan
- DISA Windows 10 STIG V3R1 Policy
- PowerShell (Native Windows 10)

---

## Skills Demonstrated

- STIG interpretation
- Windows security hardening
- Registry policy enforcement
- Compliance validation workflow
- Idempotent PowerShell automation
